---
const skills = {
  frontend: ["Astro", "Vue.js", "Tailwind CSS", "AlpineJS", "React", "HTML/CSS"],
  backend: ["PHP (Laravel)", "TypeScript", "JavaScript", "SQL Server", "MySQL"],
  tools: ["Git", "Servidores VPS", "Firebase", "Figma", "WordPress", "Email Marketing (Mailings)"]
};
---
<section id="sobre-mi" class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal-on-scroll">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Sobre Mí</h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="liquid-glass p-8 md:p-10 reveal-on-scroll delay-100">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Ingeniero en Desarrollo y Gestión de Software</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Con un enfoque Full Stack, cuento con experiencia sólida en la creación, despliegue y mantenimiento de aplicaciones web corporativas y plataformas administrativas utilizando arquitecturas modernas, así como en la gestión y envío de campañas de mailings corporativos.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Tengo capacidad demostrada para liderar proyectos desde su concepción hasta producción, priorizando el rendimiento, la escalabilidad y la entrega de valor directo al usuario final. Me considero una persona con gran capacidad para la resolución de problemas, aprendizaje rápido y excelente trabajo en equipo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="liquid-glass p-6 reveal-on-scroll delay-200">
          <h4 class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg>
            Frontend
          </h4>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {skills.frontend.map(skill => (
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full text-sm text-gray-200 transition-colors hover:bg-cyan-500/20 hover:border-cyan-500/50">{skill}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="liquid-glass p-6 reveal-on-scroll delay-300">
          <h4 class="text-blue-400 font-medium mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"></path></svg>
            Backend & Base de Datos
          </h4>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {skills.backend.map(skill => (
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full text-sm text-gray-200 transition-colors hover:bg-blue-500/20 hover:border-blue-500/50">{skill}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="liquid-glass p-6 reveal-on-scroll delay-[400ms]">
          <h4 class="text-purple-400 font-medium mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
            Herramientas
          </h4>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {skills.tools.map(skill => (
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full text-sm text-gray-200 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-500/20 hover:border-purple-500/50">{skill}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
